These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: video-games, baking
Job: bartender, police-officer
1. Job:bartender is in an even position##4
2. Job:police-officer == Hobby:baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | baking | video-games |
| Job     | police-officer    | bartender   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: lemonade, iced-tea
Sport: rowing, handball
1. Sport:rowing is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | lemonade        |
| Sport      | rowing  | handball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
