Nationality: german, spanish
1. Nationality:german is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:dubstep is on the left of Music-Genre:soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | soul |
| Nationality   | german | spanish |

